      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  익스포져산출
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3300-DATA-ENTY-RTN.

           INITIALIZE    OT-REC

      *    그룹회사코드
           MOVE  WK-H-I-GROUP-CO-CD
             TO  RJL0025-GROUP-CO-CD

      *    계좌번호－외화상품유형구분｜｜통합트레이드번호
           MOVE  WK-H-O-FC-PRDCT-PTRN-DSTCD
             TO  RJL0025-ACNO(1:3)
           MOVE  WK-H-O-INTGRA-TRD-NO
             TO  RJL0025-ACNO(4:14)

      *    기준일
           MOVE  WK-H-I-BASE-DD
             TO  RJL0025-BASE-DD

      *    기준년월
           MOVE  WK-H-I-BASE-YM
             TO  RJL0025-BASE-YM

      *    계좌중복일련번호
           ADD   CO-NUM-1              TO  WK-SEQ
           MOVE  WK-SEQ
             TO  RJL0025-ACN-DUP-SERNO

      *    고객식별자
           MOVE  WK-H-O-CUST-IDNFR
             TO  RJL0025-CUST-IDNFR

      *    고객관리번호
           MOVE  WK-H-O-CUST-MGT-NO
             TO  RJL0025-CUST-MGT-NO

      *    관리부점코드
           MOVE  WK-H-O-MGT-BRNCD
             TO  RJL0025-MGT-BRNCD

      *@  계좌적용구구분　및　모기업법인고객식별자　추출 SUB CALL
      *@  모기업법인고객식별자 ==> 차주고객식별자
      *@  해외현지법인여부
      *@  계좌적용구구분

           PERFORM  S3300-BJLCUS1-CALL-RTN
              THRU  S3300-BJLCUS1-CALL-EXT

      *   상품대분류코드
           MOVE  WK-H-O-PRDCT-LAG-CLSFI-CD
             TO  RJL0025-PRDCT-LAG-CLSFI-CD

      *   상품중분류코드
           MOVE  WK-H-O-PRDCT-MEDM-CLSFI-CD
             TO  RJL0025-PRDCT-MEDM-CLSFI-CD

      *   상품템플릿코드
           MOVE  WK-H-O-PRDCT-TMPLT-CD
             TO  RJL0025-PRDCT-TMPLT-CD

      *   상품번호
           MOVE  WK-H-O-PRDCT-NO
             TO  RJL0025-PRDCT-NO

      *   대출자격구분
           MOVE  SPACE
             TO  RJL0025-LN-QULFI-DSTCD

      *   시작년월일
           MOVE  WK-H-O-BUY-YMD
             TO  RJL0025-START-YMD

      *   만기년월일
           MOVE  WK-H-O-EXPIR-YMD
             TO  RJL0025-EXPIR-YMD

      *   종료년월일
           MOVE  SPACE
             TO  RJL0025-END-YMD

      *   상품계약상태구분
           MOVE  CO-CHA-1
             TO  RJL0025-PRDCT-C-STUS-DSTCD

      *   통화코드
           MOVE  WK-H-O-CNCYCD
             TO  RJL0025-CNCYCD

      *  통화한도(외화장부금액)
           MOVE  WK-H-O-FC-ACBK-AMT
             TO  RJL0025-CRNCY-CLAM

      *  통화잔액(외화장부금액)
           MOVE  WK-H-O-FC-ACBK-AMT
             TO  RJL0025-CRNCY-BAL

      *@-통화별　환산
           IF  WK-H-O-CNCYCD = CO-CHA-KRW

      *       명목액기준한도(외화장부금액)
               MOVE  WK-H-O-FC-ACBK-AMT
                 TO  RJL0025-TTL-AMT-BASE-CLAM

      *       명목액기준잔액(외화장부금액)
               MOVE  WK-H-O-FC-ACBK-AMT
                 TO  RJL0025-TTL-AMT-BASE-BAL

      *        BS기준잔액(외화장부금액)
               MOVE  WK-H-O-FC-ACBK-AMT
                 TO  RJL0025-BS-BASE-BAL

           ELSE
      *       통화별　원화환산금액CALCURATER
              PERFORM  S8000-BJLTGEX-CALL-RTN
                 THRU  S8000-BJLTGEX-CALL-EXT
           END-IF

      *   과목코드
           MOVE  CO-CHA-KTS
             TO  RJL0025-SBJCT-CD

      *   한도계좌여부
           MOVE  CO-CHA-0
             TO  RJL0025-LIMT-ACN-YN

      *    -------------------------------------------
      *    -개별여신만있음（한도여신／건별여신－＞계약）
      *    -                  한도(O) =잔액(O)
      *    -------------------------------------------
      *   명목액기준한도
           MOVE  RJL0025-TTL-AMT-BASE-BAL
             TO  RJL0025-TTL-AMT-BASE-CLAM
      *    -------------------------------------------

      *    TE한도환산금액
           MOVE  ZERO
             TO  RJL0025-TE-LIMT-AUC

      *    TE잔액환산금액
           MOVE  ZERO
             TO  RJL0025-TE-BAL-AUC

      *    CP한도환산금액
           MOVE  ZERO
             TO  RJL0025-INLS-GRCR-LIMT-AUC

      *    CP잔액환산금액
           MOVE  ZERO
             TO  RJL0025-INLS-GRCR-BAL-AUC

      *    CA담보제외금액
           MOVE  ZERO
             TO  RJL0025-CA-SCURTY-ECLUD-AMT

      *    CA담보환산금액
           MOVE  ZERO
             TO  RJL0025-CA-SCURTY-AUC

      *    관련테이블명
           MOVE  CO-TBL-ID
             TO  RJL0025-RELATD-TBL-NAME

      *    시스템최종처리일시
           MOVE  BICOM-TRAN-BASE-YMS
             TO  RJL0025-SYS-LAST-PRCSS-YMS

      *    시스템최종사용자번호
           MOVE  BICOM-USER-EMPID
             TO  RJL0025-SYS-LAST-UNO
           .
       S3300-DATA-ENTY-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@   DATA WRITE
