      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3300-BJLCUS1-CALL-RTN.

           INITIALIZE    XBJLCUS1-CA

      *@   그룹회사코드
           MOVE  WK-SYSIN-GROUP-CD
             TO  XBJLCUS1-I-GROUP-CO-CD

      *@   여신종류구분
           MOVE  CO-CHA-2
             TO  XBJLCUS1-I-YS-GB

      *@   관리부점코드
           MOVE  WK-H-O-MGT-BRNCD
             TO  XBJLCUS1-I-MGT-BRNCD

      *@   고객식별자
           MOVE  WK-H-O-CUST-IDNFR
             TO  XBJLCUS1-I-CUST-IDNFR

      *@   고객식별자가　없으면　＇9:기타＇로　적용
           IF  XBJLCUS1-I-CUST-IDNFR = SPACES
           THEN
                 #USRLOG  'CUST-IDNFR SPACE ACN : '
                                      WK-H-O-INTGRA-TRD-NO

                 ADD  CO-NUM-1
                  TO  WK-NO-CNT1

      *@        TE계좌고객구분
                MOVE  CO-CHA-9
                  TO  RJL0025-OVSES-LCAL-COPR-YN

      *@       해외현지법인여부
                MOVE  CO-CHA-0
                  TO  RJL0025-ACN-APLY-DSTCD

           ELSE
                ADD  CO-NUM-1
                 TO  WK-NO-CNT2

                #DYCALL BJLCUS1 YCCOMMON-CA XBJLCUS1-CA

                IF  NOT COND-XBJLCUS1-OK
                    #ERROR  XBJLCUS1-R-ERRCD
                            XBJLCUS1-R-TREAT-CD
                            XBJLCUS1-R-STAT
                    #OKEXIT CO-CHA-08
                END-IF

      *@       모기업법인고객식별자 ==>차주고객식별자
                MOVE  XBJLCUS1-O-MAMA-CC-CUST-IDNFR
                  TO  RJL0025-BRWR-CUST-IDNFR

      *@       해외현지법인여부
                MOVE  XBJLCUS1-O-OVSES-LCAL-COPR-YN
                  TO  RJL0025-OVSES-LCAL-COPR-YN

      *@       계좌적용구분
                MOVE  XBJLCUS1-O-TE-ACN-CUST-DSTCD
                  TO  RJL0025-ACN-APLY-DSTCD

           END-IF
           .
       S3300-BJLCUS1-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.

